份，點解以色列人可以復國？就係因為佢相信以色列係佢地「應許之地」，信念如一。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bc9e1559fa2da44ce12100961c2b43c7fd75f9","tid":2310858,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f23cc8de0c58bab9790ed1f750a6e8287cf4107","tid":2310858,"uid":268123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:15:37.000Z","msg":"有啲好奇實際操作<br />\n<br />\n咁本護照都有到期一日㗎<br />\n點不停轉換國家？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T22:37:06.000Z","msg":"有bno"},{"pid":"6f0da7db085655dddb58752168e86b7ad120fab4","tid":2310858,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"945f89e9ed442ead39333decbbd308eac29087c9","tid":2310858,"uid":194588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c574fc3d2baf6fc43ecb35c7c44f2eff4a5f90e9","tid":2310858,"uid":138964,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"廢話搧情唔洗多<br />\n政績呢<br />\n流亡議會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:23:51.000Z","msg":"流亡第一日就叫人交政績<br />\n你係咪個d閪老細？"},{"pid":"f269c5ac44bb532edc1338a85c8fb235b9e167ea","tid":2310858,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T00:03:47.000Z","msg":"人冇事就得，移民定流亡、申唔申請政治庇護都唔緊要，最重要嘅係你同家人嘅安全<br />\n<br />\n珍重，希望有一日喺自由嘅香港再見"},{"pid":"39d9eeb608be7c0fd147ba7d036c3bf918f5e5d8","tid":2310858,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba6fec86ab2295b92d5f91ce381f52d3f26c8111","tid":2310858,"uid":215044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T20:27:04.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n點可以喺唔移民同申請庇護既情況下係外國住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" cl